ck Legal and Andrews &amp; Thornton that you don’t sign an additional representation agreement with another law firm for your Talcum Powder case without first informing our firms. <strong>WE ARE YOUR LAWYERS</strong>, and unless and until you hear otherwise from us, you do not need to seek representation elsewhere.</li><li>A copy of your signed documents was emailed to you from <strong>Notifications</strong> (<a href="mailto:notifications@law.lawruler.net" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">notifications@law.lawruler.net</a>), with the subject line "<strong>Saddle Rock Legal Group LLC Received from </strong><strong>{!litify_pm__Intake__c.litify_pm__First_Name__c}".</strong> Keep in mind, these emails will often times go to your junk/spam folder.&nbsp;****Please let us know if you did not receive those documents by emailing us at <a href="mailto:intake@saddlerocklegal.com" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">intake@saddlerocklegal.com</a>.</li><li>These cases are difficult to litigate and often take years to reach a successful outcome, if any. We kindly ask you to be patient with the process and know we’re doing everything within our power to optimize the result for you.</li></ol><p>In the meantime, you are always welcome to reach out to us at 1-888-427-9607 or visit <a href="http://www.saddlerocklegal.com/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">www.saddlerocklegal.com</a> if you have any questions. We look forward to working with you! Our team will be in touch with next steps.</p><p><br></p><p>Your Saddle Rock Legal and Andrews &amp; Thornton team.</p><p><br></p></td>
